com.nabto.api

Class TunnelInfoResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nabto.api.TunnelInfoResult

  • public class TunnelInfoResult
extends java.lang.Object
    Result object of the function NabtoApi.tunnelInfo(Tunnel).

    If getStatus() is different from NabtoStatus.OK, the return values of all getVersion(), getTunnelState(), getLastError(), and getPort() are undefined.
